\pard\f0\fs28  ({\b a}) Subsp. {\b pallasianus} : Leaves c. 1 mm wide, linear to narrowly spathulate, ciliate in lower half. Calyx purplish; upper teeth often with hyaline margins, the median up to 1 mm and usually exceeding the others.{\i  Throughout the range of the species.}
\par

